The '''Lyra''' were an alien race. Five percent of the population of [[Kirima (Kalinda system)|Kirima]] were Lyra.

==Behind the scenes==
Lyra is also the name of a real life constellation, [[Wikipedia:Lyra|Lyra]], which holds the well known star [[Wikipedia:Vega|Vega]].

